lovable-dev integration
=======================

This file tracks the connection between this repository and the lovable.dev
visual editor. When using lovable.dev to scaffold or edit frontend components,
push changes back to the golden_era_marketplace/ directory and run the
self-healing script to ensure consistency:

  python3 super_copilot_autofix.py --process-images

